Modifications
================================================================================

This fork (maintained by Davide Meda) includes modifications to the upstream
codebase, including but not limited to:

  - Modular architecture under gen_agent/ with protocol-based interfaces
  - PostgreSQL dual-mode memory backend with Alembic migrations
  - Docker multi-stage build and CI/CD pipeline
  - Dialogue quality guards, intent packs, and legacy parity harness
  - Plan-to-POI matching with keyword fallback
  - Removal of the nested git submodule pattern (reverie/ is vendored)

See docs/architecture/UPSTREAM_RELATIONSHIP.md for integration boundaries.
